title: 'GM Street' — Marshawn's Return and Draft Sleepers (Ep. 93)
description:
The Ringer's Mike Lombardi and Tate Frazier discuss Marshawn Lynch's return to football (6:00), Richard Sherman's potential split with the Seahawks (11:00), NFL draft sleepers (18:00), and Peyton Manning's plans (26:00).
